{
  "texts": [
    "The complete workflow is depicted in Fig. 1.",
    "To investigate the association between NPIs and AD, we initially conducted preprocessing and integration of biomedical triples extracted from SemMedDB and SuppKG 33.",
    "Subsequently, we employed several graph representation models to derive the embedding information of ADInt.",
    "Ultimately, we selected the most effective model for generating hypotheses regarding and NPIs for AD and further evaluated them through the discovery patterns and RWD analysis.",
    "SemMedDB 30 is a repository of semantic triples extracted from PubMed abstracts and titles using the SemRep program 34."
  ]
}